name: SugarYield
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: SugarYield is an Insurance protocol allow users to speculate on pegged assets. Sugaryield has first mover advantage in bsc echosystem to provide cutting edge solution for stable coins believer's, we have indirect (CEX) competitors like, margin and future trading. Our mobile application is live and main-net smart contracts are integrated. Users can predict stable coins by investing sugar tokens in our vaults based on that they will win or lose. Sugar holders can also enjoy good return in our sugar farms.
